milestones.description: Dean Minors and Clay Smith's 50-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 41 between Steven Outerbridge and Borden
Ryan ten Doeschate has broken the record for most sixes (7) in ODIs for NED, going past Klaas-Jan van Noortwijk's 6
Mukuddem has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (10) for BMUDA, going past Romaine
Tim de Leede has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (19) for NED, going past Bas Zuiderent
